{"title":"教师之歌","authors":["韩志国"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"教师之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩志国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说起我们的岗位呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是多么普通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是何等的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不寻常——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛悠扬的海港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却见成群的海燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展翅翱翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有多少勇敢的船队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这欢乐的平台下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着拍天的大浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐刷刷地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竖起了远征的桅樯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机隆隆的矿山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却储存着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国最珍贵的宝藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有多少彩色的矿石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里开采和冶炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成铮亮的铆钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在精密的机床上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百灵鸟欢唱的原野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千朵万朵迎春花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竞相绽放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有多少破土的新苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里化作了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金稻、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青稞、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红高粱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花鹿雀跃的丛林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澎湃的松涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在耳边轰响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少红枫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少绿柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少白杨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里长成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立地顶天的栋梁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，谈起我们的职业哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那么平凡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是何等的高尚——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是水手长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却带领孩子们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征服了多少惊涛骇浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是设计师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却架设了多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通往真理的桥梁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是炉前工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却冶炼了多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"优质的钢锭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是医学家呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却抚平了多少孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵深处的创伤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的事业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不显赫一时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却珍藏着亿万人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情的希望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽不能永远存在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却在未来的岁月中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加倍地延长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用心血、汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和皱纹、白发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国换来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满园的春色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和遍野的花香……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}